      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 in pristine condition. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been professionally overhauled. Power is delivered through a precise six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential. The chassis displays zero subframe fatigue, and the suspension retains factory-spec kinematics for surgical handling. Finished in a flawless Carbon Black, the exterior shows no clear-coat failure, while the Nappa leather interior remains supple with no bolster wear. Preventative rod bearing replacement and a recent valve adjustment ensure this machine is mechanically turn-key and performance-ready.",
