    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 in the iconic Laguna Seca Blue over Grey Nappa leather. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since new. The exterior paint retains its factory depth and brilliance, protected by a recent ceramic coating, with zero rock chips or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the leather bolsters show no wear, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or tacky residue. Mechanically, it is flawless, with a comprehensive service history documenting every fluid change and preventative maintenance item, including the critical subframe reinforcement and VANOS service already completed. It drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership\u2014tight, responsive, and exhilarating. This is a rare opportunity to own a time-capsule E46 M3 for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
